title: BRIEF-Inteliwise signs deal to deliver its Virtual Advisor solution
text:
Sept 16 Inteliwise SA :
* Signs deal with Comarch Polska SA to deliver InteliWISE's Virtual Advisor solution to public administration unit of Komenda Glownej Ochotniczych Hufcow Pracy Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
